                    <div class="description">
                

<ul>

<li class="originalite">
<b>The originality</b>
:<br />
Feel like travelling differently, or have a lack of inspiration&nbsp;? London Incognito proposes themed day trips, custom built in order for you to realise your most unusual travel dreams… Once your thematic day has been chosen, London Incognito’s details will make all the difference. </li>

<li class="choix">
<b>The choice</b>
:<br />
&quot;With the &quot;<a href="Packages/a-la-carte-day-trip" target="_self">à la carte</a>
&quot; choice, you can participate in the organisation of your day, get inspired by selecting activities, include your own ideas and special requests, whilst relying on professionals to provide the finishing touches and complete all the arrangements for your day.</li>

<li class="tranquilite">
<b>Peace of mind</b>
:<br />
Having your day organised by London Incognito allows you to leave the tedious tasks behind. </li>

<li class="gain-temps">
<b>Time saving</b>
:<br />
Before and during your trip&nbsp;: London Incognito ensures you will fully enjoy your stay by saving you time on organisation, decisions and the sequence of your day&nbsp;! </li>

<li class="rassurance">
<b>The reassurance</b>
:<br />
Don’t worry about the language barrier, London Incognito takes responsibility for bookings, and delivers you a programme and a custom-built itinerary. </li>

<li class="liberte">
<b>The freedom</b>
:<br />
Visit London freely and enjoy full autonomy, while being organised. </li>

<li class="assurance">
<b>The assurance of enjoying the best services from the best providers</b>
:<br />
London Incognito chooses only the best venues and professionals in their field, in order to offer you the most original, unusual and unseen…</li>

</ul>

